  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-01 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This synthetic adversarial sample embeds an orphan Claim node (W-EP-01): the claim carries a thorough prose description and appears well-supported but lacks a structured prov:wasDerivedFrom link to any Evidence node.",
