      "acceptanceCriteria": "Manufactured solution or equivalent analytical verification must be demonstrated for the hemolysis transport scalar and the turbulence model implementation at MRL 5.",
      "rationale": "Method of manufactured solutions applied to the momentum and continuity equations; scalar hemolysis transport equation verified against an analytical power-law solution for simple Couette flow. Turbulence model verification limited to flat-plate benchmark; rotating-frame MMS not performed. Achieved level 3 against required level 4."
    },
