      "rationale": "GCI for NIH on fine mesh is 2.08 %, marginally exceeding the 2 % threshold for level 5. Temporal discretization error estimated at 1.4 % via time-step halving study. Combined discretization uncertainty reported at 2.6 %. Achieved level 3."
