      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative validation metrics (E%, MAPE, or equivalent) must be reported for the primary QoI with uncertainty bounds. Systematic bias must be assessed.",
      "rationale": "NIH comparison against multi-laboratory in-vitro data yields MAPE of 13.8 % across five operating points. Systematic over-prediction bias of +6.2 % observed at high-speed conditions. Velocity field comparison MAPE 7.3 %. Achieved level 3 against required level 4 due to unresolved systematic bias."
    },
