      "rationale": "FDA generic pump geometry used in validation matches COU geometry exactly. However, validation experiments cover only three of five COU operating points; the two highest-speed points (5 L/min 3 000 RPM and 6 L/min 3 200 RPM) lack experimental hemolysis data. Achieved level 3."
